n。用 workstation 可以 set bridge 張 lan 卡。<br />\n<br />\n另外可以考慮下用 virtualbox，都係果類野來。"},{"pid":"e29ec9e34e09f02f254d0ecadcd8e180589f8c4b","tid":1803181,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"行ESXi, 前面加隻router, 一部server搞掂, 如果service port冇重疊, 一粒public IP都夠用"},{"pid":"f8566ddd55a71f9e9f5584647420e7871950d3fe","tid":1803181,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都無講點解要 dedicate<br />\n點解大家 assume 咗佢只係要 host 兩個 domain?<br />\n有能力舞得掂 dedicated host 應該識得 virtualhost  multiple IP<br />\n我以為佢應該做緊 CPU bound 或者大量 local storage 先會有需要<br />\n否則 digital ocean linode 唔係會平啲咩<br />\n<br />\n利申 文科 dse 2020 負責吹水"},{"pid":"9ab939457a517b27e803551eda356e434a50eccc","tid":1803181,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"632126affd83ab5cb28d8e195e551719da9ad002","tid":1803181,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"CLS 開server用Ubuntu <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"旅發局個Server都係用Ubuntu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b1e57178dd8b169e01c44c21c5923045066261","tid":1803181,"uid":33650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e56cf27d36eeb010ed3625475d58415be8a1fdcf","tid":1803181,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"小弟想問下如果我唔想租2台server 嘅情況下有冇得租一台dedicated server 再買多粒ip 再整個vm 出黎assign 落去 可以慳返買一台機嘅錢 <br />\ngoogle 左都唔係好明個vm 要用咩版本<br />\n有冇巴絲識少少可以講解dd 比我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"你開ticket問provider啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12c62c2934bbe8b7f0793f41764837994c069e3","tid":1803181,"uid":33